<body>
  <div class="app">
    <header class="panel">
      <h1>Sudoku â€¢ KaÄŸÄ±t & KurÅŸun Kalem</h1>
      <div class="controls">
        <label for="difficulty" style="font-weight:700">Zorluk:</label>
        <select id="difficulty">
          <option value="veryeasy">Ã‡ok Kolay</option>
          <option value="easy" selected>Kolay</option>
          <option value="medium">Orta</option>
          <option value="hard">Zor</option>
        </select>
        <button id="newGame">Yeni Oyun</button>
        <button id="check">Kontrol</button>
        <button id="solve">Ã‡Ã¶z</button>
        <button id="clear">Temizle</button>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="board-wrap panel">
      <div id="board" class="board" role="grid" aria-label="Sudoku tahtasÄ±"></div>
      <div class="footer">Ä°pucu: HÃ¼creye dokun, klavye aÃ§Ä±lÄ±r. <b>0/Backspace</b> siler.</div>
    </div>

    <aside class="side">
      <div class="panel legend">
        <div class="status" id="status">HazÄ±r ðŸŽ¯</div>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Koyu</b> rakamlar: verili.</li>
          <li><b>KÄ±rmÄ±zÄ± dalga</b>: Ã§akÄ±ÅŸma.</li>
          <li>SatÄ±r/sÃ¼tun/kutu ve aynÄ± sayÄ± vurgulanÄ±r.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="panel legend">
        <b>Zorluk mantÄ±ÄŸÄ±</b>
        <div style="font-size:12px">Tam Ã§Ã¶zÃ¼m Ã¼retilir â†’ ipuÃ§larÄ± zorluÄŸa gÃ¶re kaldÄ±rÄ±lÄ±r â†’ <em>tek Ã§Ã¶zÃ¼mlÃ¼</em> doÄŸrulanÄ±r.</div>
      </div>
    </aside>
